My First Prefab - A simple Sniper Tower

There isn't much to say about this, installation notes are in the README

To use it in hammer, just take the entity tool and from the entity drop downlist switch it from "Entities" To "Prefabs" Easy No?

I'd Like to thank my friend Brad "Ins.SilentDeath[US] for keeping me from getting bored ;3

also if anyone wonders about the small filesize, it really is that small
